#set("content") {
  <h1 class='pageTitle'>Ballot Confirmation</h1>

  <div class='ballotTable'>
    <h3 class='ballotTitle'>Your Ballot</h3>
    <p class='ballotSubTitleLeft'>Election</p>
    <p class='ballutSubTitleRight'>Candidate</p>
    <p class='ballotElection'>#(election.name)</p>
    <div class='ballotCandidateHolder'>
      <h3 class='ballotCandidate'>#(candidate.name)</h3>
      <p class='ballotParty'>#(party.name)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <p>Before you cast your ballot, there are a number of things you can do to ensure that your vote is counted correctly.</p>
  <p>If you'd like more information before you proceed, you can select 'Help' in the menu bar at the bottom of this page.</p>
  <p>//Put verification things here.</p>
  
  <p>Once you're ready, select 'Cast Ballot' below.</p>
  <p class='warning'>Warning: This action is final. You will no longer be able to modify your vote after casting your ballot.</p>
  <a href='' class='selectionList'>
    <h3>Cast Ballot</h3>
  </a>
}
  
  
#embed("base")
